Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Dialogue - JP
Dialogue: 1,0:00:09.27,0:00:10.91,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,これで準備は完了
Dialogue: 1,0:00:11.15,0:00:13.66,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,いつでもこの建物を崩落させられる
Dialogue: 1,0:00:16.09,0:00:18.46,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,魔力　結構余裕あるな
Dialogue: 1,0:00:18.85,0:00:22.39,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,これなら　もしライオスたちに何かあっても　カバーできる
Dialogue: 1,0:00:23.79,0:00:25.89,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,いいんだよね　これで
Dialogue: 1,0:00:27.10,0:00:29.72,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,魔力を使い切って竜を気絶させる
Dialogue: 1,0:00:30.51,0:00:34.40,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,みんなの命を懸けて　当たるかわからない爆発魔法で狙うより
Dialogue: 1,0:00:35.00,0:00:37.69,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,建物の下敷きにしたほうがずっと確実
Dialogue: 1,0:00:39.13,0:00:40.55,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,うん　絶対このほうがいい
Dialogue: 1,0:00:42.03,0:00:43.24,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,落ち着いて
Dialogue: 1,0:00:46.85,0:00:49.36,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,私は私の仕事に集中しなくちゃ
Dialogue: 1,0:00:50.88,0:00:52.31,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,絶対成功させる
Dialogue: 1,0:00:53.60,0:00:55.14,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,待っててね　ファリン
Dialogue: 1,0:02:53.12,0:02:53.87,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,気付いた
Dialogue: 1,0:02:54.27,0:02:55.05,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,走れ
Dialogue: 1,0:02:59.71,0:03:00.93,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,速い速い
Dialogue: 1,0:03:01.54,0:03:04.66,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,ちなみに　炎竜は最速で時速60キロ
Dialogue: 1,0:03:04.76,0:03:05.92,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,先に言え
Dialogue: 1,0:03:06.38,0:03:08.48,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,地形で制御できてる　大丈夫
Dialogue: 1,0:03:09.12,0:03:10.63,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,次の角を右へ
Dialogue: 1,0:03:17.61,0:03:19.68,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,この直線で火の息を誘う
Dialogue: 1,0:03:21.10,0:03:24.96,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,竜は体内にためた燃料に舌打ちで着火することで　炎を吐く
Dialogue: 1,0:03:25.50,0:03:27.23,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,拘束したとき暴れないよう
Dialogue: 1,0:03:27.51,0:03:30.10,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,道中ですべての燃料を排出させる
Dialogue: 1,0:03:32.35,0:03:33.39,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,タンギングだ
Dialogue: 1,0:03:34.23,0:03:35.08,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,来るぞ
Dialogue: 1,0:03:39.09,0:03:40.73,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,なんて熱量だ
Dialogue: 1,0:03:41.12,0:03:41.76,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,だが
Dialogue: 1,0:03:48.09,0:03:50.49,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,鍋と魔術のおかげで耐えられる
Dialogue: 1,0:03:51.07,0:03:52.78,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,よし　これならいけ…
Dialogue: 1,0:03:55.38,0:03:56.11,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,これは
Dialogue: 1,0:03:57.45,0:03:58.76,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,鍋の熱が…
Dialogue: 1,0:03:59.27,0:04:01.01,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,均一に広がって
Dialogue: 1,0:04:02.28,0:04:03.11,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,あっつ
Dialogue: 1,0:04:12.67,0:04:14.61,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,そりゃそうだ
Dialogue: 1,0:04:15.33,0:04:18.01,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,あれで毎日センシが料理してるんだから
Dialogue: 1,0:04:18.01,0:04:20.78,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,てっきり竜の炎は特別に弾くのかと
Dialogue: 1,0:04:21.10,0:04:25.57,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,ナマリ曰く　アダマントは竜の攻撃をすべて防ぐという話だったが
Dialogue: 1,0:04:25.99,0:04:28.04,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,アイツ適当なこと言ったな
Dialogue: 1,0:04:28.26,0:04:29.15,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,言ってない
Dialogue: 1,0:04:32.82,0:04:33.73,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,また来る
Dialogue: 1,0:04:34.02,0:04:34.89,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,しかたない
Dialogue: 1,0:04:34.89,0:04:36.41,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,ルート変更だ
Dialogue: 1,0:04:44.99,0:04:45.66,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,ウソ
Dialogue: 1,0:04:46.37,0:04:47.14,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,もう来た
Dialogue: 1,0:04:47.86,0:04:48.93,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,早くない
Dialogue: 1,0:04:51.77,0:04:54.03,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,二手に分かれるって作戦は
Dialogue: 1,0:04:54.22,0:04:56.60,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,私　予定どおりやっていいの
Dialogue: 1,0:04:57.23,0:04:58.61,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,ええい　わからん
Dialogue: 1,0:04:58.88,0:05:00.15,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,もうやっちゃう
Dialogue: 1,0:05:52.16,0:05:53.45,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,ウソウソウソ
Dialogue: 1,0:05:53.45,0:05:54.83,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,まったく効いてないし
Dialogue: 1,0:05:58.13,0:05:58.77,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,動くな
Dialogue: 1,0:06:08.86,0:06:10.73,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,逆鱗がすぐそこだ
Dialogue: 1,0:06:11.56,0:06:13.16,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,あと少し踏み込めば
Dialogue: 1,0:06:13.41,0:06:14.15,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,届く
Dialogue: 1,0:06:24.67,0:06:25.15,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,に…
Dialogue: 1,0:06:26.40,0:06:28.11,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,逃げやがった
Dialogue: 1,0:06:28.69,0:06:29.83,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,クソ　ケン助
Dialogue: 1,0:06:29.83,0:06:31.31,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,やはり所詮は魔物…
Dialogue: 1,0:06:32.10,0:06:32.59,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,おま…
Dialogue: 1,0:06:32.59,0:06:34.64,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,ライオス　チルチャック　立て
Dialogue: 1,0:06:35.17,0:06:36.18,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,上だ
Dialogue: 1,0:06:37.57,0:06:38.99,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,腹部に潜り込め
Dialogue: 1,0:06:38.99,0:06:40.15,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,ライオス　テメエ
Dialogue: 1,0:06:40.15,0:06:41.93,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,悪かった　悪かったから
Dialogue: 1,0:06:42.38,0:06:45.45,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,クソ　共通語は罵倒の語彙が少なすぎる
Dialogue: 1,0:06:45.59,0:06:47.78,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,ポンザ　トロルド　ウネルマ
Dialogue: 1,0:06:47.90,0:06:50.64,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,なんだかよくわからない言語で罵られている
Dialogue: 1,0:06:50.88,0:06:52.46,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,どうすんだ　こっから
Dialogue: 1,0:06:53.71,0:06:54.41,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,怒ってる
Dialogue: 1,0:06:54.41,0:06:55.65,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,すごく怒ってる
Dialogue: 1,0:06:55.92,0:06:58.02,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,しかたない　尻尾の側から逃げ…
Dialogue: 1,0:07:01.97,0:07:03.68,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,だめだ　危険だ
Dialogue: 1,0:07:03.80,0:07:06.50,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,俺たち一生股ぐらから出られないんじゃ
Dialogue: 1,0:07:09.89,0:07:10.81,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,だめだ
Dialogue: 1,0:07:10.96,0:07:12.96,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,こんな簡単な詠唱じゃ効果がない
Dialogue: 1,0:07:13.12,0:07:13.89,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,集中
Dialogue: 1,0:07:24.10,0:07:25.44,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,何やってんだよ
Dialogue: 1,0:07:25.44,0:07:27.80,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,唯一の武器が粉々に…
Dialogue: 1,0:07:27.97,0:07:29.55,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,どうすんだ　こっから
Dialogue: 1,0:07:30.14,0:07:32.59,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,しかたない　これを使え
Dialogue: 1,0:07:33.93,0:07:37.03,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,やっぱりそれ　本当に特別な金属なのか
Dialogue: 1,0:07:37.57,0:07:40.25,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,あらゆる魔物の骨や皮をたち
Dialogue: 1,0:07:40.39,0:07:43.23,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,ワシが一日も欠かさず手入れをしてきた
Dialogue: 1,0:07:43.23,0:07:45.32,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,この世に２つとないかもしれない
Dialogue: 1,0:07:45.65,0:07:47.69,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,ミスリル製の包丁じゃ
Dialogue: 1,0:07:48.34,0:07:49.40,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,ミスリル？
Dialogue: 1,0:07:49.85,0:07:50.77,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,マジかよ
Dialogue: 1,0:07:51.54,0:07:53.33,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,ナマリに見せてやりたかった
Dialogue: 1,0:07:53.52,0:07:55.97,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,アイツ　場合によっちゃセンシを殺すぞ
Dialogue: 1,0:07:56.18,0:07:59.37,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,なんとなくそういう感じはしたので　黙っていた
Dialogue: 1,0:08:02.58,0:08:03.72,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,このっ
Dialogue: 1,0:08:05.88,0:08:07.97,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,本当にウロコを貫通した
Dialogue: 1,0:08:10.80,0:08:13.85,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,しかし　この刀身ではどこを斬りつけようが
Dialogue: 1,0:08:13.96,0:08:16.71,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,致命傷など与えることはできないのでは
Dialogue: 1,0:08:26.31,0:08:27.98,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,どうしよう　どうしよう
Dialogue: 1,0:08:28.32,0:08:30.31,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,作戦は失敗したってことだよね
Dialogue: 1,0:08:30.76,0:08:33.12,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,それとも何か別の作戦中
Dialogue: 1,0:08:33.51,0:08:35.03,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,いったいどうしたら
Dialogue: 1,0:08:37.99,0:08:39.64,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,迷ってる場合じゃない
Dialogue: 1,0:08:39.96,0:08:41.25,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,下がれ　下がれ
Dialogue: 1,0:08:42.96,0:08:45.00,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,どんどん武器が遠くなっていく
Dialogue: 1,0:08:45.95,0:08:48.62,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,このまま後退すると広場に出ちまう
Dialogue: 1,0:08:48.89,0:08:51.00,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,そしたら火の息で消し炭だ
Dialogue: 1,0:08:51.39,0:08:53.18,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,ワシが竜の気を引こう
Dialogue: 1,0:08:54.03,0:08:55.11,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,よせ　危険だ
Dialogue: 1,0:08:55.58,0:08:58.31,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,ライオス　もうわかっているだろう
Dialogue: 1,0:08:58.96,0:09:01.84,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,今までお前が食ってきた魔物の中に
Dialogue: 1,0:09:02.06,0:09:04.52,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,死力を尽くさないものがいたか
Dialogue: 1,0:09:05.09,0:09:07.37,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,ここでは　食うか食われるか
Dialogue: 1,0:09:07.37,0:09:10.32,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,必死にならなければ　食われるのはこちらだ
Dialogue: 1,0:09:11.00,0:09:12.40,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,腹をくくれ
Dialogue: 1,0:09:13.89,0:09:14.49,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,センシ
Dialogue: 1,0:09:26.73,0:09:27.14,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,セン…
Dialogue: 1,0:09:27.14,0:09:27.82,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,バカ
Dialogue: 1,0:09:28.17,0:09:30.21,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,お前が飛び出しちゃ意味ないだろ
Dialogue: 1,0:09:30.80,0:09:32.08,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,お前はいったん引け
Dialogue: 1,0:09:32.25,0:09:33.94,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,マルシルとなんとかしろ
Dialogue: 1,0:09:34.72,0:09:36.00,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,おい　生きてるか
Dialogue: 1,0:09:36.27,0:09:37.33,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,今どけてやる…
Dialogue: 1,0:09:41.49,0:09:42.50,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,動けるか
Dialogue: 1,0:09:55.77,0:09:56.54,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,やった
Dialogue: 1,0:10:02.42,0:10:03.74,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,なんか地面にくっついて…
Dialogue: 1,0:10:03.74,0:10:05.17,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,どけ
Dialogue: 1,0:10:08.18,0:10:09.21,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,ライオス
Dialogue: 1,0:10:13.26,0:10:14.60,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,すぐ戻る
Dialogue: 1,0:10:15.85,0:10:16.64,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,センシ
Dialogue: 1,0:10:16.83,0:10:17.81,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,立てって
Dialogue: 1,0:10:18.73,0:10:19.25,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,セン…
Dialogue: 1,0:10:31.08,0:10:32.36,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,すまん　マルシル
Dialogue: 1,0:10:32.65,0:10:34.11,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,こんな所にいるとは
Dialogue: 1,0:10:34.55,0:10:36.72,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,魔法効いてるみたいでよかった
Dialogue: 1,0:10:37.31,0:10:38.65,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,今どうなってるの
Dialogue: 1,0:10:38.65,0:10:39.54,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,２人は
Dialogue: 1,0:10:39.76,0:10:41.08,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,マズいことになった
Dialogue: 1,0:10:41.37,0:10:43.19,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,立てた作戦全部失敗だ
Dialogue: 1,0:10:43.63,0:10:46.25,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,２人は今　竜の足元で気絶してる
Dialogue: 1,0:10:47.17,0:10:48.88,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,どどど…　どうしよう
Dialogue: 1,0:10:49.47,0:10:51.65,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,そうか　私の魔法しかないか
Dialogue: 1,0:10:51.99,0:10:54.03,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,竜は手負いで凶暴になってる
Dialogue: 1,0:10:54.35,0:10:56.45,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,近づくのも　視野に入るのも危険だ
Dialogue: 1,0:10:56.60,0:10:58.81,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,でもでも　早くなんとかしないと
Dialogue: 1,0:10:59.49,0:11:00.40,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,上に向かう
Dialogue: 1,0:11:01.98,0:11:03.18,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,ど…　どうするの
Dialogue: 1,0:11:03.47,0:11:05.10,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,竜の顔の高さまで行って
Dialogue: 1,0:11:05.35,0:11:06.56,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,俺は鍋に乗り
Dialogue: 1,0:11:07.63,0:11:09.79,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,マルシルがそれを爆発させる
Dialogue: 1,0:11:13.41,0:11:15.10,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,竜は左目が潰れてる
Dialogue: 1,0:11:15.69,0:11:17.03,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,左側から近づけば
Dialogue: 1,0:11:17.36,0:11:19.76,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,気付かれずに飛び移ることができるはず
Dialogue: 1,0:11:20.73,0:11:21.88,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,そんな
Dialogue: 1,0:11:22.78,0:11:24.83,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,以前　マルシルも同じことをやったろう
Dialogue: 1,0:11:25.79,0:11:27.55,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,ウンディーネと戦ったとき
Dialogue: 1,0:11:28.15,0:11:31.41,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,あのときは　水と水上歩行があったから
Dialogue: 1,0:11:31.60,0:11:33.77,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,今回は防御魔法と鍋がある
Dialogue: 1,0:11:34.35,0:11:35.39,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,そのあとは
Dialogue: 1,0:11:35.55,0:11:38.39,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,頭にしがみついたままどうやって逆鱗を狙うの
Dialogue: 1,0:11:39.44,0:11:41.11,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,そこは多少考えがある
Dialogue: 1,0:11:42.96,0:11:44.48,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,もう失敗できないよ
Dialogue: 1,0:11:45.89,0:11:47.62,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,そのつもりはない
Dialogue: 1,0:11:52.69,0:11:53.73,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,本当にやるの
Dialogue: 1,0:11:54.11,0:11:55.95,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,ちゃんと策はあるんだよね
Dialogue: 1,0:11:57.09,0:11:58.39,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,信じてるからね
Dialogue: 1,0:12:28.45,0:12:29.69,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,振り落とされるぞ
Dialogue: 1,0:12:29.82,0:12:31.50,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,早く策を実行しろ
Dialogue: 1,0:12:31.96,0:12:33.58,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,一瞬で済むことだ
Dialogue: 1,0:12:34.65,0:12:36.34,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,大したことじゃない
Dialogue: 1,0:12:37.57,0:12:39.06,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,ファリンの痛みに
Dialogue: 1,0:12:40.24,0:12:41.37,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,比べれば
Dialogue: 1,0:12:44.78,0:12:45.90,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,ライオス
Dialogue: 1,0:13:51.40,0:13:52.90,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,ライオス兄ちゃん
Dialogue: 1,0:13:53.75,0:13:55.10,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,どこ行くの
Dialogue: 1,0:13:55.59,0:13:57.47,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,墓場に幽霊が出るんだって
Dialogue: 1,0:13:57.79,0:13:59.43,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,父さんたちには秘密だからな
Dialogue: 1,0:14:07.67,0:14:09.12,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,大丈夫だって
Dialogue: 1,0:14:09.56,0:14:11.62,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,あんまりくっつくと　歩きづらいだろ
Dialogue: 1,0:14:17.51,0:14:19.29,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,虫一匹いないな
Dialogue: 1,0:14:19.66,0:14:20.83,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,帰ろう　ファリン
Dialogue: 1,0:14:23.51,0:14:24.46,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,兄ちゃん
Dialogue: 1,0:14:32.31,0:14:34.15,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,兄ちゃん　兄ちゃん
Dialogue: 1,0:14:38.35,0:14:40.11,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,取ってくれ
Dialogue: 1,0:14:40.67,0:14:42.61,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,助けて
Dialogue: 1,0:14:43.03,0:14:43.89,Dialogue_JP_Alt,,0,0,0,,頼む
Dialogue: 1,0:14:44.44,0:14:45.97,Dialogue_JP_Alt,,0,0,0,,取ってくれ
Dialogue: 1,0:14:43.36,0:14:44.44,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,冷たい
Dialogue: 1,0:14:45.35,0:14:47.34,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,息ができない
Dialogue: 1,0:14:48.94,0:14:50.90,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,ファリン　逃げ…
Dialogue: 1,0:14:52.93,0:14:54.66,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,ライオス
Dialogue: 1,0:15:01.23,0:15:02.59,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,兄ちゃんを
Dialogue: 1,0:15:03.84,0:15:05.40,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,放せー
Dialogue: 1,0:15:18.37,0:15:20.35,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,そこのお墓の人
Dialogue: 1,0:15:21.13,0:15:23.33,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,指輪が魂を縛ってる
Dialogue: 1,0:15:24.11,0:15:25.36,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,取ってあげて
Dialogue: 1,0:15:26.91,0:15:28.69,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,霊は解放される
Dialogue: 1,0:15:29.86,0:15:30.78,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,指輪？
Dialogue: 1,0:15:31.64,0:15:32.60,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,いったい…
Dialogue: 1,0:15:33.45,0:15:36.32,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,これ　先日死んだオルマンの墓だ
Dialogue: 1,0:15:36.63,0:15:40.76,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,生前よく自慢してた　エルフから金の指輪を買ったと
Dialogue: 1,0:15:41.55,0:15:43.84,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,なぜそんなことを　あの子どもは
Dialogue: 1,0:15:47.29,0:15:49.61,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,私何か悪いことした
Dialogue: 1,0:15:50.41,0:15:52.17,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,すごいことだよ　ファリン
Dialogue: 1,0:15:52.50,0:15:54.59,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,お前は霊術の才能があるんだ
Dialogue: 1,0:15:55.64,0:15:56.61,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,気にすんな
Dialogue: 1,0:15:57.04,0:15:58.93,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,大人は魔法が怖いもんだ
Dialogue: 1,0:15:59.85,0:16:02.18,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,ファリンはちゃんとした魔法を勉強したらいい
Dialogue: 1,0:16:02.63,0:16:04.10,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,仕事に困らないぞ
Dialogue: 1,0:16:04.48,0:16:05.36,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,仕事？
Dialogue: 1,0:16:05.46,0:16:06.41,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,そうだな
Dialogue: 1,0:16:06.69,0:16:08.86,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,司祭とか　墓守とか
Dialogue: 1,0:16:09.16,0:16:11.50,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,旅の除霊師ってのもおもしろそうだな
Dialogue: 1,0:16:14.13,0:16:17.53,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,外国を渡り歩いて　困ってる人を助けるんだ
Dialogue: 1,0:16:18.28,0:16:19.34,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,楽しそう
Dialogue: 1,0:16:19.72,0:16:22.03,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,そしたら兄ちゃんも一緒に来てくれる
Dialogue: 1,0:16:22.23,0:16:23.19,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,もっちろん
Dialogue: 1,0:16:23.48,0:16:24.78,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,どんな国に行ってみたい
Dialogue: 1,0:16:27.01,0:16:28.62,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,海が見たいな
Dialogue: 1,0:16:29.37,0:16:30.58,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,砂漠でもいい
Dialogue: 1,0:16:30.97,0:16:33.56,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,砂漠には喋る犬の国があるらしい
Dialogue: 1,0:16:34.52,0:16:36.13,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,絶対行きたい
Dialogue: 1,0:16:37.38,0:16:38.23,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,でも…
Dialogue: 1,0:16:39.09,0:16:42.18,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,もう一緒には行かないほうがいいかもしれないね
Dialogue: 1,0:16:43.07,0:16:43.77,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,ファリン
Dialogue: 1,0:16:44.43,0:16:45.37,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,どうして
Dialogue: 1,0:16:46.93,0:16:48.53,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,気にしなくていいの
Dialogue: 1,0:16:49.95,0:16:52.55,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,さよなら　ライオス兄さん
Dialogue: 1,0:16:56.06,0:16:57.71,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,ライオス　大丈夫
Dialogue: 1,0:16:58.41,0:17:00.22,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,ひとまず止血だけしておくから
Dialogue: 1,0:17:00.39,0:17:01.75,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,もう少し我慢してね
Dialogue: 1,0:17:02.12,0:17:03.61,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,私　２人を探してくる
Dialogue: 1,0:17:03.77,0:17:04.74,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,あと　脚も
Dialogue: 1,0:17:07.38,0:17:09.64,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,「気にしないで」か
Dialogue: 1,0:17:10.88,0:17:13.34,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,そんな悲しいこと言うなよ
Dialogue: 1,0:17:14.33,0:17:17.13,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,絶対に連れて帰るからな
Dialogue: 1,0:17:20.17,0:17:21.77,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,チルチャック
Dialogue: 1,0:17:22.21,0:17:23.71,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,センシ
Dialogue: 1,0:17:25.33,0:17:26.02,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,いた
Dialogue: 1,0:17:27.08,0:17:28.36,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,よかった
Dialogue: 1,0:17:28.77,0:17:29.65,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,大丈夫…
Dialogue: 1,0:17:30.20,0:17:31.44,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,じゃないよね
Dialogue: 1,0:17:32.53,0:17:35.56,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,私も　防御魔法もっと練習しなきゃな
Dialogue: 1,0:17:35.83,0:17:39.15,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,まっ　破裂してないだけ上出来だ
Dialogue: 1,0:17:39.56,0:17:42.42,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,トロンサム　ルナァエ　スタンティヌス
Dialogue: 1,0:17:42.93,0:17:44.67,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,ユーレカント　ウーンズゥ
Dialogue: 1,0:17:46.04,0:17:48.76,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,いってえ
Dialogue: 1,0:17:49.51,0:17:51.60,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,余計苦しんでないか
Dialogue: 1,0:17:51.74,0:17:55.01,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,大ケガを短時間で治すと　回復痛がね
Dialogue: 1,0:17:55.19,0:17:58.08,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,大丈夫　ちゃんと治ってる証しだから
Dialogue: 1,0:17:58.29,0:17:59.57,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,じゃあ　次はセンシ
Dialogue: 1,0:17:59.57,0:18:00.64,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,ワシはいい
Dialogue: 1,0:18:00.64,0:18:02.21,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,自分で治す
Dialogue: 1,0:18:02.21,0:18:03.92,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,何か月かかるの
Dialogue: 1,0:18:04.13,0:18:06.39,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,ファリンは回復魔法が得意だったけど
Dialogue: 1,0:18:06.39,0:18:09.19,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,でも私だって　早さには自信があるの
Dialogue: 1,0:18:09.41,0:18:12.28,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,そ…　それが痛みの原因では
Dialogue: 1,0:18:15.81,0:18:17.12,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,ライオース
Dialogue: 1,0:18:17.58,0:18:18.91,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,ほら　足出して
Dialogue: 1,0:18:23.88,0:18:25.59,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,ブリトレイトウームス
Dialogue: 1,0:18:25.89,0:18:27.05,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,ルナァエ　アクトゥム
Dialogue: 1,0:18:27.34,0:18:29.16,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,アスバム　ヒストゥム　エレス
Dialogue: 1,0:18:29.33,0:18:30.96,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,ユーレカント　ウーンズゥ
Dialogue: 1,0:18:33.94,0:18:35.24,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,くっついた
Dialogue: 1,0:18:38.09,0:18:39.86,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,足の中がかゆい
Dialogue: 1,0:18:39.86,0:18:41.48,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,回復痛　回復痛
Dialogue: 1,0:18:41.93,0:18:44.05,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,よくやったな　ライオス
Dialogue: 1,0:18:44.66,0:18:47.31,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,本当に炎竜を倒しおった
Dialogue: 1,0:18:47.79,0:18:49.28,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,みんなのおかげだ
Dialogue: 1,0:18:49.48,0:18:51.94,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,誰一人欠けてもこの勝ちはなかった
Dialogue: 1,0:18:52.30,0:18:54.82,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,一時はどうなることかと思ったけど
Dialogue: 1,0:18:55.06,0:18:57.03,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,さすがに肝が冷えた
Dialogue: 1,0:18:57.33,0:18:59.33,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,想定が少し甘かったな
Dialogue: 1,0:18:59.67,0:19:02.26,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,まっ　勝てりゃいいんだ　勝てりゃ
Dialogue: 1,0:19:03.17,0:19:03.78,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,ただ
Dialogue: 1,0:19:04.40,0:19:05.65,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,ほれ　ライオス
Dialogue: 1,0:19:06.14,0:19:06.87,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,ケン助
Dialogue: 1,0:19:07.28,0:19:10.09,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,その件については　まだ許してないからな
Dialogue: 1,0:19:10.57,0:19:12.52,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,あとでゆっくり話をさせろ
Dialogue: 1,0:19:12.99,0:19:13.46,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 1,0:19:14.87,0:19:15.70,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,さて
Dialogue: 1,0:19:16.21,0:19:18.38,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,腹の中身を確認してみよう
Dialogue: 1,0:19:28.29,0:19:29.64,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,分厚い皮膚
Dialogue: 1,0:19:29.95,0:19:31.57,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,これじゃ包丁で戦っても
Dialogue: 1,0:19:31.57,0:19:33.63,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,皮下脂肪にすら届かないわけだ
Dialogue: 1,0:19:34.33,0:19:37.55,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,しかし　胃に辿りつくまで一仕事だな
Dialogue: 1,0:19:37.75,0:19:39.14,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,発破かけてみる
Dialogue: 1,0:19:39.67,0:19:42.74,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,竜もさすがに内臓は他の生き物と同じだ
Dialogue: 1,0:19:43.21,0:19:45.39,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,少しずつ肉を掘りながら進もう
Dialogue: 1,0:19:54.28,0:19:55.46,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,あばら骨だ
Dialogue: 1,0:19:55.69,0:19:57.57,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,少し迂回して掘り進めよう
Dialogue: 1,0:20:00.98,0:20:03.47,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,暗いな　ランタンをつけるか
Dialogue: 1,0:20:03.47,0:20:04.36,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,火はだめだ
Dialogue: 1,0:20:04.83,0:20:06.32,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,マルシル　明かりを
Dialogue: 1,0:20:16.48,0:20:17.80,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,あっつ
Dialogue: 1,0:20:18.54,0:20:21.45,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,炭鉱で働いていた時代を思い出すな
Dialogue: 1,0:20:23.56,0:20:24.57,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,これは
Dialogue: 1,0:20:25.22,0:20:26.37,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,胃袋だ
Dialogue: 1,0:20:30.04,0:20:30.69,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,よし
Dialogue: 1,0:20:31.28,0:20:32.15,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,開くぞ
Dialogue: 1,0:20:41.99,0:20:42.87,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,空…
Dialogue: 1,0:20:43.96,0:20:44.98,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,そんな
Dialogue: 1,0:20:46.14,0:20:47.68,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,違う竜なんじゃないの
Dialogue: 1,0:20:48.12,0:20:49.16,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,それはない
Dialogue: 1,0:20:49.60,0:20:52.91,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,目の上の傷は確かにあのときの竜と同じものだ
Dialogue: 1,0:20:54.61,0:20:59.43,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,縄張り意識の強いオスが　こんな近くに何匹もいるとは考えにくいし
Dialogue: 1,0:21:00.24,0:21:02.19,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,念のため腸もさらってみよう
Dialogue: 1,0:21:04.19,0:21:07.07,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,ほ…　骨の一片も残ってないなんて
Dialogue: 1,0:21:07.54,0:21:09.86,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,急いで　フンを探さなきゃ
Dialogue: 1,0:21:11.74,0:21:14.84,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,不眠で動き続けたことで消化が進んだか
Dialogue: 1,0:21:18.55,0:21:19.28,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,そうか
Dialogue: 1,0:21:39.47,0:21:40.46,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,何これ
Dialogue: 1,0:21:41.31,0:21:43.06,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,毛や骨の塊だよ
Dialogue: 1,0:21:43.68,0:21:45.61,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,獲物を丸飲みする動物の一部は
Dialogue: 1,0:21:45.61,0:21:48.05,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,消化しにくいものをまとめて吐き出すんだ
Dialogue: 1,0:21:49.07,0:21:52.85,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,炎竜はそれを吐き出さず　炎の息の燃料にする
Dialogue: 1,0:21:53.65,0:21:56.48,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,この黒い毛は何匹か魔狼を食ってるな
Dialogue: 1,0:21:57.03,0:21:57.87,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,それに…
Dialogue: 1,0:22:01.79,0:22:03.25,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,か…　髪の毛
Dialogue: 1,0:22:04.01,0:22:04.90,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,それって…
Dialogue: 1,0:22:05.21,0:22:06.05,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,ほぐしてみよう
Dialogue: 1,0:22:06.60,0:22:08.62,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,人骨が混じっているかもしれない
Dialogue: 1,0:22:12.41,0:22:14.54,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,なあ　この棒って
Dialogue: 1,0:22:16.12,0:22:17.63,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,ちょっと　ライオス
Dialogue: 1,0:22:17.93,0:22:18.82,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,この杖
Dialogue: 1,0:22:23.97,0:22:24.65,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,ファ…
Dialogue: 1,0:22:26.49,0:22:27.47,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,ファリン
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Dialogue - CN
Dialogue: 2,0:00:09.27,0:00:10.91,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,這樣就準備好了
Dialogue: 2,0:00:11.15,0:00:13.66,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,可以隨時讓這建築崩塌
Dialogue: 2,0:00:16.09,0:00:18.46,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,魔力還很充足
Dialogue: 2,0:00:18.85,0:00:22.39,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,這下就算萊歐斯他們出現了意外 我也能幫一下
Dialogue: 2,0:00:23.79,0:00:25.89,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,這樣應該沒有問題吧
Dialogue: 2,0:00:27.10,0:00:29.72,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,用盡所有的魔力 讓龍昏迷
Dialogue: 2,0:00:30.51,0:00:34.40,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,比起需要大家拼命 還不知道能不能命中的爆炸魔法
Dialogue: 2,0:00:35.00,0:00:37.69,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,把龍埋在建築下面的方案穩妥多了
Dialogue: 2,0:00:39.13,0:00:40.55,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,嗯 這個方案要好多了
Dialogue: 2,0:00:42.03,0:00:43.24,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,冷靜一些
Dialogue: 2,0:00:46.85,0:00:49.36,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,我必須完成好自己的任務
Dialogue: 2,0:00:50.88,0:00:52.31,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,一定要成功
Dialogue: 2,0:00:53.60,0:00:55.14,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,等著我 法琳
Dialogue: 2,0:02:53.12,0:02:53.87,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,發現我們了
Dialogue: 2,0:02:54.27,0:02:55.05,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,快跑
Dialogue: 2,0:02:59.71,0:03:00.93,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,也太快了
Dialogue: 2,0:03:01.54,0:03:04.66,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,順便一提 紅龍最快時速60公里
Dialogue: 2,0:03:04.76,0:03:05.92,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,你早說啊
Dialogue: 2,0:03:06.38,0:03:08.48,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,牠受到地形的限制 沒事
Dialogue: 2,0:03:09.12,0:03:10.63,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,下個路口右轉
Dialogue: 2,0:03:17.61,0:03:19.68,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,在這直道引誘牠噴火
Dialogue: 2,0:03:21.10,0:03:24.96,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,龍通過咂嘴點燃體內的燃料 進而噴火
Dialogue: 2,0:03:25.50,0:03:27.23,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,防止牠被控制住以後發狂
Dialogue: 2,0:03:27.51,0:03:30.10,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,要讓牠在路上吐出所有的燃料
Dialogue: 2,0:03:32.35,0:03:33.39,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,舌頭動了
Dialogue: 2,0:03:34.23,0:03:35.08,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,要噴火了
Dialogue: 2,0:03:39.09,0:03:40.73,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,好強的熱浪
Dialogue: 2,0:03:41.12,0:03:41.76,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 2,0:03:48.09,0:03:50.49,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,能藉助鍋和魔法抗住
Dialogue: 2,0:03:51.07,0:03:52.78,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,好 這樣下去…
Dialogue: 2,0:03:55.38,0:03:56.11,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,這是…
Dialogue: 2,0:03:57.45,0:03:58.76,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,鍋的熱量…
Dialogue: 2,0:03:59.27,0:04:01.01,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,均勻擴散…
Dialogue: 2,0:04:02.28,0:04:03.11,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,好燙
Dialogue: 2,0:04:12.67,0:04:14.61,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,那還用說嗎
Dialogue: 2,0:04:15.33,0:04:18.01,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,先西每天都在用那東西做飯
Dialogue: 2,0:04:18.01,0:04:20.78,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,還以為能排斥龍的火焰呢
Dialogue: 2,0:04:21.10,0:04:25.57,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,娜瑪莉不是說 精金能夠防禦住龍的所有攻擊
Dialogue: 2,0:04:25.99,0:04:28.04,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,那傢伙隨便亂說是吧
Dialogue: 2,0:04:28.26,0:04:29.15,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,我沒說
Dialogue: 2,0:04:32.82,0:04:33.73,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,又要來了
Dialogue: 2,0:04:34.02,0:04:34.89,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,沒辦法
Dialogue: 2,0:04:34.89,0:04:36.41,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,改變路線
Dialogue: 2,0:04:44.99,0:04:45.66,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 2,0:04:46.37,0:04:47.14,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,這就來了
Dialogue: 2,0:04:47.86,0:04:48.93,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,有點快啊
Dialogue: 2,0:04:51.77,0:04:54.03,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,不是打算分頭行動嗎
Dialogue: 2,0:04:54.22,0:04:56.60,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,我按照計劃行動就行嗎
Dialogue: 2,0:04:57.23,0:04:58.61,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,好煩 不管了
Dialogue: 2,0:04:58.88,0:05:00.15,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,我直接動手
Dialogue: 2,0:05:52.16,0:05:53.45,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,騙人的吧
Dialogue: 2,0:05:53.45,0:05:54.83,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,完全沒效果啊
Dialogue: 2,0:05:58.13,0:05:58.77,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,不要動
Dialogue: 2,0:06:08.86,0:06:10.73,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,逆鱗就在跟前
Dialogue: 2,0:06:11.56,0:06:13.16,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,再向前走一點
Dialogue: 2,0:06:13.41,0:06:14.15,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,就夠了
Dialogue: 2,0:06:24.67,0:06:25.15,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,怎…
Dialogue: 2,0:06:26.40,0:06:28.11,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,怎麼逃走了
Dialogue: 2,0:06:28.69,0:06:29.83,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,該死 劍助
Dialogue: 2,0:06:29.83,0:06:31.31,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,魔物終究是魔物…
Dialogue: 2,0:06:32.10,0:06:32.59,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,你…
Dialogue: 2,0:06:32.59,0:06:34.64,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,萊歐斯 奇爾查克 起來
Dialogue: 2,0:06:35.17,0:06:36.18,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,看上面
Dialogue: 2,0:06:37.57,0:06:38.99,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,去肚子下面
Dialogue: 2,0:06:38.99,0:06:40.15,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,萊歐斯 你這傢伙
Dialogue: 2,0:06:40.15,0:06:41.93,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,怪我 是我不好
Dialogue: 2,0:06:42.38,0:06:45.45,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,該死 通用語言罵人的話太少了
Dialogue: 2,0:06:45.59,0:06:47.78,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,Ponza Toroldo Unerma!
Dialogue: 2,0:06:47.90,0:06:50.64,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,怎麼開始用我不懂的語言罵我了
Dialogue: 2,0:06:50.88,0:06:52.46,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,接下來怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 2,0:06:53.71,0:06:54.41,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,生氣了
Dialogue: 2,0:06:54.41,0:06:55.65,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,牠真的好生氣
Dialogue: 2,0:06:55.92,0:06:58.02,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,沒辦法了 從尾巴旁邊溜出…
Dialogue: 2,0:07:01.97,0:07:03.68,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,不行 好危險
Dialogue: 2,0:07:03.80,0:07:06.50,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,要一輩子走不出這兩腿之間了
Dialogue: 2,0:07:09.89,0:07:10.81,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 2,0:07:10.96,0:07:12.96,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,這麼簡單的咒語沒有效果
Dialogue: 2,0:07:13.12,0:07:13.89,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,專心
Dialogue: 2,0:07:24.10,0:07:25.44,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,你做甚麼啊
Dialogue: 2,0:07:25.44,0:07:27.80,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,唯一的武器都碎了…
Dialogue: 2,0:07:27.97,0:07:29.55,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,接下來怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 2,0:07:30.14,0:07:32.59,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,沒辦法了 拿去用吧
Dialogue: 2,0:07:33.93,0:07:37.03,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,那真是用特殊金屬製作的嗎
Dialogue: 2,0:07:37.57,0:07:40.25,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,斬斷任何魔物的骨與皮
Dialogue: 2,0:07:40.39,0:07:43.23,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,我日復一日 從未忘記打磨
Dialogue: 2,0:07:43.23,0:07:45.32,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,這世上或許僅此一把
Dialogue: 2,0:07:45.65,0:07:47.69,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,秘銀製作的菜刀
Dialogue: 2,0:07:48.34,0:07:49.40,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,秘銀?
Dialogue: 2,0:07:49.85,0:07:50.77,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 2,0:07:51.54,0:07:53.33,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,真想給娜瑪莉看看
Dialogue: 2,0:07:53.52,0:07:55.97,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,那傢伙搞不好會殺了先西啊
Dialogue: 2,0:07:56.18,0:07:59.37,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,我隱約有那樣的預感 所以就沒提起
Dialogue: 2,0:08:02.58,0:08:03.72,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,混蛋
Dialogue: 2,0:08:05.88,0:08:07.97,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,真的刺穿了鱗片
Dialogue: 2,0:08:10.80,0:08:13.85,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,不過這刀就這麼點 不管砍哪個位置
Dialogue: 2,0:08:13.96,0:08:16.71,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,怎麼想都無法造成致命傷吧
Dialogue: 2,0:08:26.31,0:08:27.98,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,怎麼辦 怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 2,0:08:28.32,0:08:30.31,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,看起來計劃是失敗了?
Dialogue: 2,0:08:30.76,0:08:33.12,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,還是說在執行其他方案?
Dialogue: 2,0:08:33.51,0:08:35.03,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,該怎麼辦才好
Dialogue: 2,0:08:37.99,0:08:39.64,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,沒有時間猶豫了
Dialogue: 2,0:08:39.96,0:08:41.25,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,退後 退後
Dialogue: 2,0:08:42.96,0:08:45.00,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,武器離我們越來越遠
Dialogue: 2,0:08:45.95,0:08:48.62,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,再向後就要到廣場上了
Dialogue: 2,0:08:48.89,0:08:51.00,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,一口火就給我們噴成渣
Dialogue: 2,0:08:51.39,0:08:53.18,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,我來吸引龍的注意力
Dialogue: 2,0:08:54.03,0:08:55.11,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,別 太危險
Dialogue: 2,0:08:55.58,0:08:58.31,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,萊歐斯 你該明白了吧
Dialogue: 2,0:08:58.96,0:09:01.84,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,你過去吃下的所有魔物
Dialogue: 2,0:09:02.06,0:09:04.52,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,哪個不是拼盡了全力
Dialogue: 2,0:09:05.09,0:09:07.37,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,在這裡 不是吃就是被吃
Dialogue: 2,0:09:07.37,0:09:10.32,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,如果不竭盡全力 我們就是淪為食物的一方
Dialogue: 2,0:09:11.00,0:09:12.40,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,咬緊牙關
Dialogue: 2,0:09:13.89,0:09:14.49,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,先西
Dialogue: 2,0:09:26.73,0:09:27.14,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,先…
Dialogue: 2,0:09:27.14,0:09:27.82,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,蠢貨
Dialogue: 2,0:09:28.17,0:09:30.21,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,你跑出去還有甚麼意義
Dialogue: 2,0:09:30.80,0:09:32.08,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,你先撤退
Dialogue: 2,0:09:32.25,0:09:33.94,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,和瑪露希爾想想辦法
Dialogue: 2,0:09:34.72,0:09:36.00,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,喂 還活著嗎
Dialogue: 2,0:09:36.27,0:09:37.33,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,我拉你出來…
Dialogue: 2,0:09:41.49,0:09:42.50,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,能動嗎
Dialogue: 2,0:09:55.77,0:09:56.54,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,成功了
Dialogue: 2,0:10:02.42,0:10:03.74,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,怎麼好像粘到地上…
Dialogue: 2,0:10:03.74,0:10:05.17,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,讓開
Dialogue: 2,0:10:08.18,0:10:09.21,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,萊歐斯
Dialogue: 2,0:10:13.26,0:10:14.60,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,我馬上回來
Dialogue: 2,0:10:15.85,0:10:16.64,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,先西
Dialogue: 2,0:10:16.83,0:10:17.81,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,站起來
Dialogue: 2,0:10:18.73,0:10:19.25,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,先…
Dialogue: 2,0:10:31.08,0:10:32.36,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,抱歉 瑪露希爾
Dialogue: 2,0:10:32.65,0:10:34.11,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,沒想到你在這裡
Dialogue: 2,0:10:34.55,0:10:36.72,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,還好 看來我的魔法還有效
Dialogue: 2,0:10:37.31,0:10:38.65,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,現在甚麼情況
Dialogue: 2,0:10:38.65,0:10:39.54,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,他們兩個呢
Dialogue: 2,0:10:39.76,0:10:41.08,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,情況變得很不妙
Dialogue: 2,0:10:41.37,0:10:43.19,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,所有計劃都失敗了
Dialogue: 2,0:10:43.63,0:10:46.25,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,他們兩個倒在了龍跟前
Dialogue: 2,0:10:47.17,0:10:48.88,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,怎怎… 怎麼辦
Dialogue: 2,0:10:49.47,0:10:51.65,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,這樣嗎 只有我的魔法了
Dialogue: 2,0:10:51.99,0:10:54.03,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,龍受了傷 現在很狂躁
Dialogue: 2,0:10:54.35,0:10:56.45,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,靠近或是進入牠的視線都很危險
Dialogue: 2,0:10:56.60,0:10:58.81,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,可如果不抓緊時間的話…
Dialogue: 2,0:10:59.49,0:11:00.40,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,去上面
Dialogue: 2,0:11:01.98,0:11:03.18,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,要… 要做甚麼
Dialogue: 2,0:11:03.47,0:11:05.10,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,到龍頭部的高度
Dialogue: 2,0:11:05.35,0:11:06.56,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,我站在鍋裡
Dialogue: 2,0:11:07.63,0:11:09.79,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,瑪露希爾對鍋使用爆炸魔法
Dialogue: 2,0:11:13.41,0:11:15.10,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,龍的左眼已經瞎了
Dialogue: 2,0:11:15.69,0:11:17.03,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,從左側靠近的話
Dialogue: 2,0:11:17.36,0:11:19.76,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,應該可以趁牠沒察覺跳上去
Dialogue: 2,0:11:20.73,0:11:21.88,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,這也太…
Dialogue: 2,0:11:22.78,0:11:24.83,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,瑪露希爾之前也做過同樣的事吧
Dialogue: 2,0:11:25.79,0:11:27.55,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,與溫蒂妮戰鬥的時候
Dialogue: 2,0:11:28.15,0:11:31.41,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,那時有水 還有水上行走的魔法
Dialogue: 2,0:11:31.60,0:11:33.77,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,這次有防禦魔法和鍋
Dialogue: 2,0:11:34.35,0:11:35.39,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,那接下來呢
Dialogue: 2,0:11:35.55,0:11:38.39,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,你抱在牠的頭上 怎麼瞄準逆鱗
Dialogue: 2,0:11:39.44,0:11:41.11,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,我有個主意
Dialogue: 2,0:11:42.96,0:11:44.48,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,沒有失敗的餘地了
Dialogue: 2,0:11:45.89,0:11:47.62,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,我會成功
Dialogue: 2,0:11:52.69,0:11:53.73,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,真的要來嗎
Dialogue: 2,0:11:54.11,0:11:55.95,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,真的想好辦法了嗎
Dialogue: 2,0:11:57.09,0:11:58.39,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,我相信你
Dialogue: 2,0:12:28.45,0:12:29.69,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,要被甩出去了
Dialogue: 2,0:12:29.82,0:12:31.50,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,必須趕快動手
Dialogue: 2,0:12:31.96,0:12:33.58,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,一瞬間就能完成
Dialogue: 2,0:12:34.65,0:12:36.34,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,沒甚麼大不了的
Dialogue: 2,0:12:37.57,0:12:39.06,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,比起法琳的痛
Dialogue: 2,0:12:40.24,0:12:41.37,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,不算甚麼
Dialogue: 2,0:12:44.78,0:12:45.90,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,萊歐斯
Dialogue: 2,0:13:51.40,0:13:52.90,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,萊歐斯哥哥
Dialogue: 2,0:13:53.75,0:13:55.10,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,你要去哪裡
Dialogue: 2,0:13:55.59,0:13:57.47,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,聽說墓地裡有幽靈出現
Dialogue: 2,0:13:57.79,0:13:59.43,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,不要告訴爸爸他們哦
Dialogue: 2,0:14:07.67,0:14:09.12,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,沒事的
Dialogue: 2,0:14:09.56,0:14:11.62,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,你抱得這麼緊 我怎麼走路
Dialogue: 2,0:14:17.51,0:14:19.29,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,蟲子都沒見一隻
Dialogue: 2,0:14:19.66,0:14:20.83,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,回去吧 法琳
Dialogue: 2,0:14:23.51,0:14:24.46,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 2,0:14:32.31,0:14:34.15,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,哥哥 哥哥
Dialogue: 2,0:14:38.35,0:14:40.11,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,幫我取掉
Dialogue: 2,0:14:40.67,0:14:42.61,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,救我
Dialogue: 2,0:14:43.03,0:14:43.89,Dialogue_CN_Alt,,0,0,0,,拜託了
Dialogue: 2,0:14:44.44,0:14:45.97,Dialogue_CN_Alt,,0,0,0,,幫我取掉
Dialogue: 2,0:14:43.36,0:14:44.44,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,好冷
Dialogue: 2,0:14:45.35,0:14:47.34,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,無法呼吸
Dialogue: 2,0:14:48.94,0:14:50.90,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,法琳 快逃
Dialogue: 2,0:14:52.93,0:14:54.66,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,萊歐斯
Dialogue: 2,0:15:01.23,0:15:02.59,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,把哥哥
Dialogue: 2,0:15:03.84,0:15:05.40,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,放開
Dialogue: 2,0:15:18.37,0:15:20.35,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,那邊墓裡的人
Dialogue: 2,0:15:21.13,0:15:23.33,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,戒指束縛了靈魂
Dialogue: 2,0:15:24.11,0:15:25.36,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,幫他取下來
Dialogue: 2,0:15:26.91,0:15:28.69,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,靈魂會得到解脫
Dialogue: 2,0:15:29.86,0:15:30.78,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,戒指?
Dialogue: 2,0:15:31.64,0:15:32.60,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,究竟…
Dialogue: 2,0:15:33.45,0:15:36.32,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,這是前幾天去世的奧爾曼的墓
Dialogue: 2,0:15:36.63,0:15:40.76,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,生前經常炫耀 說從精靈那買來了金戒指
Dialogue: 2,0:15:41.55,0:15:43.84,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,那個孩子怎麼會知道…
Dialogue: 2,0:15:47.29,0:15:49.61,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,我做了壞事嗎
Dialogue: 2,0:15:50.41,0:15:52.17,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,很厲害呀 法琳
Dialogue: 2,0:15:52.50,0:15:54.59,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,你有使用靈術的才能
Dialogue: 2,0:15:55.64,0:15:56.61,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,不用在意
Dialogue: 2,0:15:57.04,0:15:58.93,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,大人都害怕魔法
Dialogue: 2,0:15:59.85,0:16:02.18,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,法琳去好好學習一下魔法就行
Dialogue: 2,0:16:02.63,0:16:04.10,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,不愁沒有工作
Dialogue: 2,0:16:04.48,0:16:05.36,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,工作?
Dialogue: 2,0:16:05.46,0:16:06.41,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,我想想
Dialogue: 2,0:16:06.69,0:16:08.86,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,司祭 要麼守墓人?
Dialogue: 2,0:16:09.16,0:16:11.50,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,做個四處旅行的除靈師也很有趣吧
Dialogue: 2,0:16:14.13,0:16:17.53,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,在國外四處遊歷 幫助有困難的人
Dialogue: 2,0:16:18.28,0:16:19.34,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,好像很有意思
Dialogue: 2,0:16:19.72,0:16:22.03,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,那哥哥也會與我一起去嗎
Dialogue: 2,0:16:22.23,0:16:23.19,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,那當然
Dialogue: 2,0:16:23.48,0:16:24.78,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,你想去甚麼樣的國家
Dialogue: 2,0:16:27.01,0:16:28.62,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,想看看大海
Dialogue: 2,0:16:29.37,0:16:30.58,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,沙漠也不錯
Dialogue: 2,0:16:30.97,0:16:33.56,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,聽說沙漠裡有會說話的狗的國家
Dialogue: 2,0:16:34.52,0:16:36.13,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,我想去看看
Dialogue: 2,0:16:37.38,0:16:38.23,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,不過…
Dialogue: 2,0:16:39.09,0:16:42.18,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,我們或許不該再一同踏上旅途了
Dialogue: 2,0:16:43.07,0:16:43.77,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,法琳
Dialogue: 2,0:16:44.43,0:16:45.37,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,為甚麼
Dialogue: 2,0:16:46.93,0:16:48.53,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,不用在意我
Dialogue: 2,0:16:49.95,0:16:52.55,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,再見了 萊歐斯哥哥
Dialogue: 2,0:16:56.06,0:16:57.71,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,萊歐斯 沒事吧
Dialogue: 2,0:16:58.41,0:17:00.22,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,我先幫你止一下血
Dialogue: 2,0:17:00.39,0:17:01.75,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,你再堅持一會
Dialogue: 2,0:17:02.12,0:17:03.61,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,我去找他們兩個
Dialogue: 2,0:17:03.77,0:17:04.74,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,還有你的腿
Dialogue: 2,0:17:07.38,0:17:09.64,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,「不用在意我」嗎
Dialogue: 2,0:17:10.88,0:17:13.34,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,不要說這麼悲傷的話
Dialogue: 2,0:17:14.33,0:17:17.13,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,我一定會帶你回去
Dialogue: 2,0:17:20.17,0:17:21.77,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,奇爾查克
Dialogue: 2,0:17:22.21,0:17:23.71,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,先西
Dialogue: 2,0:17:25.33,0:17:26.02,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,你在這
Dialogue: 2,0:17:27.08,0:17:28.36,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 2,0:17:28.77,0:17:29.65,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,沒事…
Dialogue: 2,0:17:30.20,0:17:31.44,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,看起來不像
Dialogue: 2,0:17:32.53,0:17:35.56,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,我還需要好好練習一下防禦魔法
Dialogue: 2,0:17:35.83,0:17:39.15,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,身體沒破裂已經算是很好了
Dialogue: 2,0:17:39.56,0:17:42.42,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,Tronsum Lunaae Stantinus
Dialogue: 2,0:17:42.93,0:17:44.67,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,Eurekant Oonzu
Dialogue: 2,0:17:46.04,0:17:48.76,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 2,0:17:49.51,0:17:51.60,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,他是不是更痛苦了
Dialogue: 2,0:17:51.74,0:17:55.01,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,短時間內治癒大傷 會有恢復痛
Dialogue: 2,0:17:55.19,0:17:58.08,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,不用擔心 這說明是治好了
Dialogue: 2,0:17:58.29,0:17:59.57,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,現在該先西了
Dialogue: 2,0:17:59.57,0:18:00.64,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,我就算了
Dialogue: 2,0:18:00.64,0:18:02.21,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,我自己能好
Dialogue: 2,0:18:02.21,0:18:03.92,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,要花幾個月啊
Dialogue: 2,0:18:04.13,0:18:06.39,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,法琳很擅長恢復的魔法
Dialogue: 2,0:18:06.39,0:18:09.19,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,但比速度 我還是有信心的
Dialogue: 2,0:18:09.41,0:18:12.28,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,這… 這就是痛苦的原因…
Dialogue: 2,0:18:15.81,0:18:17.12,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,萊歐斯
Dialogue: 2,0:18:17.58,0:18:18.91,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,來 把腿抬起來
Dialogue: 2,0:18:23.88,0:18:25.59,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,Britrayeums
Dialogue: 2,0:18:25.89,0:18:27.05,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,Lunae Actum
Dialogue: 2,0:18:27.34,0:18:29.16,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,Asbam Histum Eres
Dialogue: 2,0:18:29.33,0:18:30.96,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,Eurekant Ounzu
Dialogue: 2,0:18:33.94,0:18:35.24,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,接上了
Dialogue: 2,0:18:38.09,0:18:39.86,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,腿裡面好癢
Dialogue: 2,0:18:39.86,0:18:41.48,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,恢復痛 恢復痛
Dialogue: 2,0:18:41.93,0:18:44.05,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,你做得不錯 萊歐斯
Dialogue: 2,0:18:44.66,0:18:47.31,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,真的把紅龍打敗了
Dialogue: 2,0:18:47.79,0:18:49.28,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,多虧了大家
Dialogue: 2,0:18:49.48,0:18:51.94,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,少了誰這場戰鬥都無法勝利
Dialogue: 2,0:18:52.30,0:18:54.82,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,之前都差點就以為要完蛋了
Dialogue: 2,0:18:55.06,0:18:57.03,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,捏了一把冷汗
Dialogue: 2,0:18:57.33,0:18:59.33,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,計劃還是欠考慮了
Dialogue: 2,0:18:59.67,0:19:02.26,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,算了 贏了就行 贏了就好
Dialogue: 2,0:19:03.17,0:19:03.78,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,不過
Dialogue: 2,0:19:04.40,0:19:05.65,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,拿好 萊歐斯
Dialogue: 2,0:19:06.14,0:19:06.87,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,劍助
Dialogue: 2,0:19:07.28,0:19:10.09,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,關於這件事 我可還沒有原諒你
Dialogue: 2,0:19:10.57,0:19:12.52,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,之後我們好好談談
Dialogue: 2,0:19:12.99,0:19:13.46,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 2,0:19:14.87,0:19:15.70,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 2,0:19:16.21,0:19:18.38,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,檢查一下肚子裡面吧
Dialogue: 2,0:19:28.29,0:19:29.64,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,好厚的皮膚
Dialogue: 2,0:19:29.95,0:19:31.57,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,拿著菜刀來戰鬥
Dialogue: 2,0:19:31.57,0:19:33.63,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,確實連皮下脂肪都碰不到
Dialogue: 2,0:19:34.33,0:19:37.55,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,看這樣想走到胃裡也不容易啊
Dialogue: 2,0:19:37.75,0:19:39.14,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,爆破一下試試?
Dialogue: 2,0:19:39.67,0:19:42.74,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,龍的內臟也與其他生物的差不多
Dialogue: 2,0:19:43.21,0:19:45.39,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,一邊挖肉一邊前進吧
Dialogue: 2,0:19:54.28,0:19:55.46,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,是肋骨
Dialogue: 2,0:19:55.69,0:19:57.57,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,我們換個方向繞一下吧
Dialogue: 2,0:20:00.98,0:20:03.47,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,好黑 點個提燈吧
Dialogue: 2,0:20:03.47,0:20:04.36,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,不能用火
Dialogue: 2,0:20:04.83,0:20:06.32,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,瑪露希爾 照明
Dialogue: 2,0:20:16.48,0:20:17.80,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,好熱
Dialogue: 2,0:20:18.54,0:20:21.45,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,回想起了在煤礦工作的日子
Dialogue: 2,0:20:23.56,0:20:24.57,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,這是…
Dialogue: 2,0:20:25.22,0:20:26.37,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,是胃
Dialogue: 2,0:20:30.04,0:20:30.69,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 2,0:20:31.28,0:20:32.15,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,打開看看
Dialogue: 2,0:20:41.99,0:20:42.87,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,空的…
Dialogue: 2,0:20:43.96,0:20:44.98,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,怎麼會
Dialogue: 2,0:20:46.14,0:20:47.68,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,找錯龍了?
Dialogue: 2,0:20:48.12,0:20:49.16,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,這不會
Dialogue: 2,0:20:49.60,0:20:52.91,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,眼睛上方的傷與那時的龍一模一樣
Dialogue: 2,0:20:54.61,0:20:59.43,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,地盤意識這麼強的雄性 這附近應該不會同時出現好幾頭
Dialogue: 2,0:21:00.24,0:21:02.19,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,保險起見 腸子也掏一遍吧
Dialogue: 2,0:21:04.19,0:21:07.07,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,連… 連一塊骨頭都沒剩下…
Dialogue: 2,0:21:07.54,0:21:09.86,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,抓緊時間 去看看糞便
Dialogue: 2,0:21:11.74,0:21:14.84,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,不睡覺一直活動 所以消化很快嗎
Dialogue: 2,0:21:18.55,0:21:19.28,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,這樣嗎
Dialogue: 2,0:21:39.47,0:21:40.46,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,這是甚麼
Dialogue: 2,0:21:41.31,0:21:43.06,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,一團頭髮與骨頭
Dialogue: 2,0:21:43.68,0:21:45.61,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,有些將獵物整個吞下的動物
Dialogue: 2,0:21:45.61,0:21:48.05,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,會將難以消化的部分集中吐出去
Dialogue: 2,0:21:49.07,0:21:52.85,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,但紅龍不會吐 而是用來做吐息的燃料
Dialogue: 2,0:21:53.65,0:21:56.48,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,這黑毛是吃了幾頭座狼
Dialogue: 2,0:21:57.03,0:21:57.87,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,還有…
Dialogue: 2,0:22:01.79,0:22:03.25,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,是… 是頭髮
Dialogue: 2,0:22:04.01,0:22:04.90,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,這麼說…
Dialogue: 2,0:22:05.21,0:22:06.05,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,攤開看看吧
Dialogue: 2,0:22:06.60,0:22:08.62,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,或許裡面有人的骨頭
Dialogue: 2,0:22:12.41,0:22:14.54,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,我說 這根棒子…
Dialogue: 2,0:22:16.12,0:22:17.63,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,過來看看 萊歐斯
Dialogue: 2,0:22:17.93,0:22:18.82,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,這法杖
Dialogue: 2,0:22:23.97,0:22:24.65,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,法…
Dialogue: 2,0:22:26.49,0:22:27.47,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,法琳?
Comment: 0,0:16:39.77,0:16:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Screen
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,OP
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.33,0:01:09.09,Meshi_OPJP,,0,0,0,,外から窓をくぐった光が　床に作った最初の友達
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.09,0:01:16.39,Meshi_OPJP,,0,0,0,,空っぽの手を容易く取られて　連れ出されてから夢の中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.39,0:01:24.06,Meshi_OPJP,,0,0,0,,幾つかの普通が重なり合うと　時々そこには魔法が宿る
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.06,0:01:31.53,Meshi_OPJP,,0,0,0,,あれは恐らく悪魔だった　あれから醒めない夢の中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.07,0:01:35.33,Meshi_OPJP,,0,0,0,,籠の中　鳥が鳴いて気付いた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.78,0:01:40.87,Meshi_OPJP,,0,0,0,,失くしていた事　もう引き返せない事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.67,0:01:50.09,Meshi_OPJP,,0,0,0,,どうして体は生きたがるの　心に何を求めているの
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.09,0:01:57.64,Meshi_OPJP,,0,0,0,,肺が吸い込んだ　続きの世界　何度でも吐いた　命の証
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.64,0:02:05.19,Meshi_OPJP,,0,0,0,,さあ今　鍵が廻る音　探し物が囁くよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.19,0:02:13.36,Meshi_OPJP,,0,0,0,,赤い血が巡る　その全てで　見えない糸を手繰り寄せて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.33,0:01:09.09,Meshi_OPCN,,0,0,0,,窗外的一縷光線灑落地面 是最初的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.09,0:01:16.39,Meshi_OPCN,,0,0,0,,空無一物的手就這樣被握緊 啟程便是夢境之中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.39,0:01:24.06,Meshi_OPCN,,0,0,0,,一次次平凡的遭遇 魔法也時而蘊藏其中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.06,0:01:31.53,Meshi_OPCN,,0,0,0,,那恐怕便是惡魔 從此便是難以甦醒的夢境
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.07,0:01:35.33,Meshi_OPCN,,0,0,0,,籠中的鳥兒啼鳴 回過神來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.78,0:01:40.87,Meshi_OPCN,,0,0,0,,失去的事物 無法挽回的事物
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.67,0:01:50.09,Meshi_OPCN,,0,0,0,,為何身體不肯放棄生存 內心在嚮往甚麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.09,0:01:57.64,Meshi_OPCN,,0,0,0,,用力吸氣 今後的世界 無數次吐氣 生命的證明
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.64,0:02:05.19,Meshi_OPCN,,0,0,0,,現在鑰匙轉動的聲音響起 尋找之物就在前方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.19,0:02:13.36,Meshi_OPCN,,0,0,0,,血液湧上 一切的一切 收起無法看見的絲線
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,ED
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.58,0:22:37.04,Meshi_EDJP,,888,0,0,,{\blur2}君のためのパーティーだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.68,0:22:47.39,Meshi_EDJP,,0,1070,0,,{\blur2}どこから話すべきかな
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.39,0:22:52.73,Meshi_EDJP,,0,1070,0,,{\blur2}君にはそういつも救われてきたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.73,0:22:59.23,Meshi_EDJP,,0,820,1,,{\blur2}だから今日こそはとびきりをプレゼント
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.19,0:23:01.99,Meshi_EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}さぁ始めるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.49,0:23:04.78,Meshi_EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}着慣れてないドレスコード
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.78,0:23:07.78,Meshi_EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}お馴染みの顔がお出迎え
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.83,0:23:10.16,Meshi_EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}君のこと
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.16,0:23:12.79,Meshi_EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}みんなが想っているんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.79,0:23:14.12,Meshi_EDJP,,0,777,1,,{\blur2}Full-course session
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.12,0:23:16.50,Meshi_EDJP,,0,777,1,,{\blur2}※リアクションはノンフィクション
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.50,0:23:18.50,Meshi_EDJP,,0,777,1,,{\blur2}ボナペティート！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.80,0:23:23.76,Meshi_EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}「ありがとう」じゃ足らんなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.76,0:23:26.51,Meshi_EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}それ以上なら何だっていい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.76,0:23:29.76,Meshi_EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}ただ君に伝われ！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.76,0:23:31.64,Meshi_EDJP,,0,777,0,,{\blur2}ふざけ合って笑う時も
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.64,0:23:34.52,Meshi_EDJP,,0,777,0,,{\blur2}涙こぼれそうな夜も
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.52,0:23:37.52,Meshi_EDJP,,0,777,0,,{\blur2}君のための仲間だ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.52,0:23:39.48,Meshi_EDJP,,777,0,0,,{\blur2}それはどんな魔法だって
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.48,0:23:42.36,Meshi_EDJP,,777,0,0,,{\blur2}超えるような希望のフレイバー
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.53,0:23:45.28,Meshi_EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}ただ君が笑うだけ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.28,0:23:47.36,Meshi_EDJP,,0,777,0,,{\blur2}だから今日は騒いだって
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.36,0:23:50.28,Meshi_EDJP,,0,777,0,,{\blur2}誰も文句は言わせない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.28,0:23:52.99,Meshi_EDJP,,888,0,0,,{\blur2}君のためのパーティーだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.99,0:23:56.54,Meshi_EDJP,,888,0,0,,{\blur2}楽しもうよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.12,0:23:59.88,Meshi_EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\an8\blur2}いいから跳んじゃって！
Comment: 0,0:22:31.58,0:22:33.58,Meshi_EDCN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.58,0:22:37.04,Meshi_EDCN,,888,0,0,,都是為你準備的聚會
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.68,0:22:47.39,Meshi_EDCN,,0,1070,0,,該從何處說起呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.39,0:22:52.73,Meshi_EDCN,,0,1070,0,,一路總是得到你的拯救
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.73,0:22:59.23,Meshi_EDCN,,0,820,1,,所以今天要送你一份驚喜
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.19,0:23:01.99,Meshi_EDCN,,0,0,0,,那開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.49,0:23:04.78,Meshi_EDCN,,0,0,0,,不習慣的衣著打扮
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.78,0:23:07.78,Meshi_EDCN,,0,0,0,,熟悉的朋友前來迎接
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.83,0:23:10.16,Meshi_EDCN,,0,0,0,,你的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.16,0:23:12.79,Meshi_EDCN,,0,0,0,,大家何時曾經忘記
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.79,0:23:14.12,Meshi_EDCN,,0,777,1,,Full-course session
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.12,0:23:16.50,Meshi_EDCN,,0,777,1,,※反應並非虛構
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.50,0:23:18.50,Meshi_EDCN,,0,777,1,,用餐愉快
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.80,0:23:23.76,Meshi_EDCN,,0,0,0,,「謝謝」還不足夠
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.76,0:23:26.51,Meshi_EDCN,,0,0,0,,在此之上怎樣都好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.76,0:23:29.76,Meshi_EDCN,,0,0,0,,只要理解便好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.76,0:23:31.64,Meshi_EDCN,,0,777,0,,打鬧也好歡笑也好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.64,0:23:34.52,Meshi_EDCN,,0,777,0,,打溼眼眶的夜晚也好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.52,0:23:37.52,Meshi_EDCN,,0,777,0,,大家都是你的夥伴
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.52,0:23:39.48,Meshi_EDCN,,777,0,0,,無論怎樣的魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.48,0:23:42.36,Meshi_EDCN,,777,0,0,,都難比擬的希望的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.53,0:23:45.28,Meshi_EDCN,,0,0,0,,只要看到你的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.28,0:23:47.36,Meshi_EDCN,,0,777,0,,今天就盡情喧鬧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.36,0:23:50.28,Meshi_EDCN,,0,777,0,,沒有人能有意見
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.28,0:23:52.99,Meshi_EDCN,,888,0,0,,都是為你準備的聚會
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.99,0:23:56.54,Meshi_EDCN,,888,0,0,,開心盡興吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.12,0:23:59.88,Meshi_EDCN,,0,0,0,,就來跳起來吧
